  <brief_title>Single Dose CHG Pharmacokinetic Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single Dose Pharmacokinetic Study to Assess the Systemic Exposure of Chlorhexidine From ReadyPrep® CHG (2% Chlorhexidine Gluconate Cloth)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
