  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A single 2% topical application of ReadyPrep® CHG was applied on either the abdomen
      (Treatment-1) or the groin (Treatment-2) whereas Treatment-3 consisted of a control treatment
      where the same procedure as Treatment-1 and -2 was performed, but without the topical
      application of ReadyPrep® CHG. The treatments were separated by a wash-out of 7 calendar
      days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
